# Test back space typing
Output examples/svgs/backspace.svg

Set FontSize 16
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[32m$\x1b[0m "
Set Template macos
Set Theme github-dark
Set Watermark "\x1b[0;2mby tool3\x1b[0m"

Type "echo 'I am an idiot savant developer'"
Left 10
Sleep 200ms
Backspace 7
Sleep 1s
Backspace 10
Space
Type "a "

Sleep 100ms

Screenshot examples/svgs/backspace_out.svg

Enter
Sleep 300ms
